OL,3,CThird of teachers are physically
OL,4,Cabused by pupils at school
OL,6,FReport by ITV News Social Affairs
OL,7,FCorrespondent Sarah Corker and
OL,8,FProducer Lottie Kilraine
OL,10,FBethan Drew was a primary school
OL,11,Fteacher for 22 years, but last year
OL,12,Fshe quit the job she loved after a
OL,13,Fpupil kicked her, causing lasting
OL,14,Fdamage.
OL,16,F"I was writing on our little
OL,17,Fwhiteboard and a child had become
OL,18,Fextremely dysregulated and kicked me
OL,19,Fin the side," she told ITV News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
