OL,6,F"I ended up having damage to my
OL,7,Fkidney, which has resulted in lots of
OL,8,Finfection."
OL,10,FListing some of the other injuries she
OL,11,Fhad suffered in the classroom, Ms Drew
OL,12,Fadded: "I had earrings pulled out and
OL,13,Fripped, black eyes where I was
OL,14,Fheadbutted, lots of scratches, lots of
OL,15,Fbites."
OL,17,FAn exclusive survey for ITV News
OL,18,Freveals that a third of teachers have
OL,19,Fbeen physically abused by a pupil in
OL,20,Fthe last year.
