OL,6,FA third of teachers have been
OL,7,Fphysically abused by pupils at school,
OL,8,FITV News Social Affairs Correspondent
OL,9,FSarah Corker explains
OL,11,FTeacher Tapp, a survey app
OL,12,Fspecifically designed for teachers,
OL,13,Fcollected data from nearly 8,000
OL,14,Fteachers.
OL,16,FAlmost one third (29%) of those
OL,17,Fsurveyed had been physically abused by
OL,18,Fa pupil, and the majority of physical
OL,19,Fabuse (44%) took place in a primary
OL,20,Fschool.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
