OL,3,CThird of teachers are physically
OL,4,Cabused by pupils at school
OL,6,FOf those surveyed, 60% have been
OL,7,Fverbally abused by students. The abuse
OL,8,Fisn't limited to the classroom or
OL,9,Fpupils, as 40% of teachers surveyed
OL,10,Fsaid they had been verbally abused by
OL,11,Fparents.
OL,13,F"When I started, violence against
OL,14,Fteachers in school was really rare, it
OL,15,Fwas an unusual thing," Ms Drew said.
OL,17,F"I was injured lots of days, it was
OL,18,Falmost the expectation it was going to
OL,19,Fhappen. Coming home everyday and my
OL,20,Ffamily seeing me covered in cuts and
OL,21,Fbruises wasn't great.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
