OL,6,F"It was a battle because I knew these
OL,7,Fchildren weren't deliberately trying
OL,8,Fto hurt me. I wanted to help them as
OL,9,Fmuch as I could, but I just felt in
OL,10,Fthe end I couldn't do what I should
OL,11,Fhave been doing for them because of
OL,12,Fthat.
OL,14,F"I do feel sad that I left, but in the
OL,15,Fend I have to look after my health."
OL,17,FViolence against teachers is just one
OL,18,Fof the factors impacting teacher
OL,19,Fretention, with the number of teachers
OL,20,Fquitting the profession currently at a
OL,21,Frecord high.
