OL,6,FIn the last school year alone, almost
OL,7,F40,000 teachers have left the sector,
OL,8,Fwhile vacancies have more than doubled
OL,9,Fsince 2010 ` with nearly 3,000 posts
OL,10,Favailable.
OL,12,FTeachers on the Isle of Sheppey in
OL,13,FKent went on strike in November 2023
OL,14,Fafter threats and violence from pupils
OL,15,Fhave made the school "unsafe".
