OL,6,FSince the Covid-19 pandemic, behaviour
OL,7,Fin the classroom has deteriorated,
OL,8,Fprompting a wave of local strikes
OL,9,Facross England. Funding pressures and
OL,10,Fcutbacks have left teachers
OL,11,Foverwhelmed, and children not getting
OL,12,Fthe help they desperately need.
OL,14,FWe showed our findings to Pepe
OL,15,FDi'lasio who is the General Secretary
OL,16,Fof the Association of Schools and
OL,17,FCollege leaders.
OL,19,F"We have definitely seen an increase
OL,20,Fin poor behaviour since Covid," he
OL,21,Ftold ITV News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
