OL,6,FPepe Di'lasio, General Secretary of
OL,7,Fthe Association of Schools and College
OL,8,Fleaders, told us there has been an
OL,9,Fincrease in poor behaviour since the
OL,10,Fpandemic
OL,12,F"For many young people, it's about
OL,13,Fhaving mental health support because
OL,14,Fthey are exhibiting behaviours as a
OL,15,Fresult of how they are feeling and we
OL,16,Fneed to be able to get to the bottom
OL,17,Fof that. But at the moment we don't
OL,18,Fhave the specialist support to do
OL,19,Fthat."
