OL,6,FThere are long delays for ADHD and
OL,7,Fautism assessments, with some children
OL,8,Fwaiting years for a diagnosis, which
OL,9,Fis needed to unlock extra funding and
OL,10,Fsupport in the classroom. There are
OL,11,Falso shortages of psychological and
OL,12,Fspecialist support staff, and this has
OL,13,Fserious consequences in the classroom.
OL,15,FHannah Abrahams, an Educational and
OL,16,FChild Psychologist, told ITV News: "So
OL,17,Fmany children just aren't getting the
OL,18,Fsupport they need because the system
OL,19,Fis totally overwhelmed.
